processVariable.name: instanceDetails

TWComponent.script: tw.local.sqlString select LS."NAME" as SnapshotName, LP.SHORT_NAME as ProjectAcronym, LBI.BPD_INSTANCE_ID as instanceID, LBI.INSTANCE_NAME as instanceName, LBI.BPD_REF as BPDReferenceID, lbsc.NAME as executionStatus, LBI.TIP as isTip, LBI.CREATE_DATETIME as createdDateTime, LUX.USER_NAME as startedByUserName, LBI.BPD_NAME as BPDName, LP.NAME as applicationName from lsw_bpd_instance lbi, LSW_PROJECT lp, LSW_SNAPSHOT ls, LSW_USR_XREF lux, LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES lbsc where LBI.SNAPSHOT_ID = LS.SNAPSHOT_ID and LS.PROJECT_ID = LP.PROJECT_ID and LBI.STARTER_ID = LUX.USER_ID(+) and LBI.EXECUTION_STATUS = LBSC.STATUS_ID and (UPPER(LBI.INSTANCE_NAME) like ? or UPPER(LUX.USER_NAME) like ? or UPPER(LBI.BPD_NAME) like ? or LBI.BPD_INSTANCE_ID = ? or LBI.BPD_REF = ? or UPPER(LP.NAME) like ? or UPPER(lbsc.name) like ? or UPPER(LS.NAME) like ? or UPPER(LP.SHORT_NAME) like ?) order by lbi.create_datetime DESC
